"2 pounds small red potatoes","  Salt and pepper","2 tablespoons red wine vinegar","2  ribs celery, finely chopped (about 1/2 cup)","3  scallions, white and light green parts only, finely chopped","1 tablespoon minced seeded chipotle chiles in adobo sauce","1/2 cup finely chopped fresh parsley","3 tablespoons olive oil"